ess &quot;Accept&quot; if you agree with the rules mentioned below. You will then be able to register.</p>\n				\n<p>Even though administrators and moderators from {lang}{PAGE_TITLE}{/lang} try to delete or edit all the unwanted posts, it is impossible for them to check all the posts. All the posts express the opinion of the author, the owners of {lang}{PAGE_TITLE}{/lang} and WoltLab GmbH (the developers of Burning Board) cannot be held responsible for the content of those posts.</p>\n\n<p>By registering, you agree not to post messages that are vulgar, impolite, disrespectful or that express (extreme) political views or (verbal) law offences.</p>\n\n<p>Additionally, the Administrators and Moderators of this board can edit or even delete your account for any reason.</p>\n\n<p>Enjoy your stay at {lang}{PAGE_TITLE}{/lang}!</p>',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4894,3,'wcf.user.register.disclaimer.button.accept','Accept',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4895,3,'wcf.user.register.disclaimer.button.decline','Decline',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4896,3,'wcf.user.register.disclaimer.title','Disclaimer',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4897,3,'wcf.user.register.email.description','Please enter your e-mail address!',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4898,3,'wcf.user.register.error.disabled','The registration is currently disabled.',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4899,3,'wcf.user.register.error.userAlreadyEnabled','This user has already been enabled.',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4900,3,'wcf.user.register.invitation','Register now!',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4901,3,'wcf.user.register.needActivation','Thank you for registering, {$username}. An e-mail with your account data has been sent to {$email}.<br />\nTo complete your registration you need to follow the link in this e-mail.',0,NULL,0,36,16),(4902,3,'wcf.user.register.needActivation.mail','Dear {$username},\n\nthank you for registering at {PAGE_TITLE}. To enable your registration, you have to take one last step.\n\nPlease click on the following link to finish your registration:\n{PAGE_URL}/index.php?page=Register&action=a&u={$userID