	<p>You can read more about this topic at the following websites:</p>\n		<ul>\n			<li><a href=\"http://www.coppa.org\" class=\"externalURL\">http://www.coppa.org</a></li>\n			<li><a href=\"http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/edcams/coppa/index.html\" class=\"externalURL\">http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/edcams/coppa/index.html</a></li>\n			<li><a href=\"http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/buspubs/coppa.shtm\" class=\"externalURL\">http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/buspubs/coppa.shtm</a></li>\n			<li><a href=\"http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/buspubs/coppakit.pdf\" class=\"externalURL\">http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/buspubs/coppakit.pdf</a><br />(A comprehensive e-booklet that outlines how to be COPPA compliant.)</li>\n		</ul>\n		<p>Children registering on your site will be shown a form where they can fill out profile fields, in addition to entering information about their parent or legal guardian.  Once completed, this form is printed out, signed by the parent or legal guardian, and returned via facsimile or postal mail.  Receipt of the completed document authorizes you to activate the child\'s account (via clicking an appropriate button).</p>\n		<p>Be sure to enter a valid postal address, facsimile number (optional), and email address to ensure that the completed COPPA document can be successfully returned.</p>',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12853,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_address','Name and address',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12854,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_address.description','Please enter the name and postal address.',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12855,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_deletion_time','Automatic deletion time',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12856,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_deletion_time.description','Enter the number of days when user accounts will be automatically deleted if you haven\'t received a parental permission. Enter 0 to stop automatic deletion.',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12857,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_email_address','E-Mail',0,NULL,0,7,28),(12858,3,'wcf.acp.option.coppa_email_address.description','Enter an e-